     <div type="to_the_reader">
   <head>TO THE READER,</head>
   <p>I Have studied to make all the answers short in these three Catechismes, for the helpe of thy memorie: First to <hi>know,</hi> and then to <hi>doe,</hi> is perfect Christianitie.</p>
